/* README */
plm is a simple compiler using a core part of PL0 
and implemented in c++.
this plmcore has a basic part of plm for easy to look at.
plm aims for expanding PL0, that we can use it. 
syntax of plm looks more like c/c++.
codings are very straight, fits to the one who wants to make 
a compiler for the first time.
expanded one is called plmmed which is medium sized plm.
Look at it, Expand it, Modify it, As you like.
plm is LEMA.

